WEBVTT

00:10:28.392 --> 00:10:30.094
kwa sababu nilipigana kuisambaza.

00:10:31.204 --> 00:10:33.447
Hakukua na umbali
ambao nisingeenda

00:10:33.471 --> 00:10:34.627
kuhubiri injili hii,

00:10:34.651 --> 00:10:37.487
kupata watu zaidi kuamini

00:10:37.511 --> 00:10:39.910
ili tuweze kufunga majeraha
ya nchi iliyovunjika,

00:10:39.934 --> 00:10:42.091
biashara moja ya kijamii kwa mda.

00:10:43.116 --> 00:10:46.289
Lakini ilikua hii safari ya uinjilisti

00:10:47.239 --> 00:10:49.497
ilionipeleka kwenye injili tofauti

00:10:50.136 --> 00:10:52.772
ambayo nimekuja kuwashirikisha leo.

00:10:53.867 --> 00:10:57.079
Ilianza jioni moja, karibia mwaka uliopita

00:10:58.199 --> 00:11:01.393
kwenye Makumbusho ya Asili ya Historia
ya jiji la New York,